# create layout
- create empty solution with dotnet nwe sln -n <yourname>
- create web api with dotnet new webapi -n <yourname>
- create classlib with dotnet new classlib -n <yourname>.Application
- create classlib with dotnet new classlib -n <yourname>.Domain
- create classlib with dotnet new classlib -n <yourname>.Persistence

# add dependensicy in sln 
- dotnet sln add API
- dotnet sln add Application
- dotnet sln add Domain
- dotnet sln add Persistence